    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "A village without any people is kinda creepy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Well, I should start my investigation. Where should I start?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's...<CR>The spectacled man!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "It's you... Don't call me by such a weird name."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry, I don't know your name. But what a coincidence to meet you here!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Coincidence...? Considering the peculiarities of this place, I'd prefer to think it was inevitable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Huh? So is the disappearance of these villagers related to Nio...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I told you, I'm not the one who should be searching for that answer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But my sister's life is at stake!<CR>She might be living through some<CR>scary nightmare somewhere..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "If you know something, please tell me, umm, M-Mr. Spectacles."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "...It's Keithgriff! Just call me Keith."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I can't stand being called such weird names."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Mr. Keith, umm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Sorry, but I'm not good at being friendly, so if you'll excuse me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "So these villagers are somehow related to Nio..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I can't stand around like this.<CR>I need to investigate!"
        }
    ]
}